elements.text:
V2 Features:
 - Element square
 - Advanced stats
 - Advanced abilities
 - Stat curve on characters

* Eneymies drop exp / coins / monkey money (prem currency)
* Characters have progression in levels
 -> The higher level the character, will increase all stats
* Character Duplicates will upgrade characters to shinies (Modifier to all stats/
  maybe stronger abilities). Also maybe there are multiple tiers of shinies ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
* Eneymies are floor based, every X floors you get a boss, if you kill a boss you get a
  a checkpoint. If you die you go back to your last checkpoint.
* On rails experience 🚂🚂🚂🚂
random enemies of increasing difficulty are costantly spawned

V1 Features:
 - Auto battling
 - Character select screen
 - Gacha screen
 - Character details screen
 - Basic abilities
 - Basic stats
 - Basic animation
 - Subset of sprites (not all 1000)
 - Levelling up
 - Difficulty increase
 - Restart at checkpoint when dying
 - Floors: Bosses/Checkpoints
